{"tid":799286,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"投票 你出世到今時今日利是錢加埋超唔超過十萬","createTime":"2018-08-30T03:04:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T07:19:16.000Z","uid":113000,"like":8,"dislike":90,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"edf4bfed7fd3daeafe27df9652ef0656a40b6c7b","tid":799286,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:04:19.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98bab94f2de6e607a88c603df78ea0b4d5cd433","tid":799286,"uid":70771,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:06:30.000Z","msg":"過硬十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7402b5eed55209cf929761654b1a22a989ac0446","tid":799286,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:09:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180829/s00001/1535548509638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180829%2Fs00001%2F1535548509638&d=hish3n5imNMdkaJsD%2FkDtZnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=ae4af217\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180829%2Fs00001%2F1535548509638&h=62322c95\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180829/s00001/1535548509638</a><br />\n<br />\n理財「應使則使」　劉鳴煒：10歲生日收10萬現金，全部存銀行 (21:53)<br />\n<br />\n今晚播出的港台電視節目《講錢。講呢啲》，邀請青年發展委員會副主席、華人置業主席劉鳴煒訪問。主持任美貞問，當一個人金錢多得花不完，理財目的何在？劉鳴煒說，理財可以是個人紀律的延伸，沒有人希望身家「少咗幾個零」：「當你有細路仔、有屋企人、有想照顧的人，自然會想慢慢增值。」<br />\n<br />\n劉鳴煒在節目中提到，家庭教育教曉自己「應使則使，應慳則慳」。他記得10歲生日當天，父母給他10萬元現金，他此後半年一元也沒花過，只是天天或隔日在數鈔票，最後存進與母親開設的聯名戶口。他說，當年不懂投資，但至少知道不應該亂花錢。<br />\n<br />\n他強調不喜歡炒炒賣賣，投資計劃短則3年，長的可達7年、10年。他又分享自己「輸得最慘一次」，是2000年左右未及脫離科網泡沫，在歐美市場損手，雖然沒有變「牆紙」，事後會反省為何察覺不到：「金融史是有教育意義的，人性會不斷重覆。」"},{"pid":"64fa166addd80521c6cb5c9b6918a817e48ccac9","tid":799286,"uid":29270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a98bab94f2de6e607a88c603df78ea0b4d5cd433","tid":799286,"uid":70771,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:06:30.000Z","msg":"過硬十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:10:00.000Z","msg":"十萬越南盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"738fffed162698d5941aca23c45ceda4957b76a3","tid":799286,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:15:57.000Z","msg":"80 年代十萬好好洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a61fb3e00e3e17b2f071fa3c1b5a4e67a1094693","tid":799286,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:35:04.000Z","msg":"1vs22<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1b8790e319052515426be7a22cf6bc4fbb6e64","tid":799286,"uid":146976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7402b5eed55209cf929761654b1a22a989ac0446","tid":799286,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T03:09:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180829/s00001/1535548509638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180829%2Fs00001%2F1535548509638&d=hish3n5imNMdkaJsD%2FkDtZnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=ae4af217\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180829%2Fs00001%2F1535548509638&h=62322c95\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180829/s00001/1535548509638</a><br />\n<br />\n理財「應使則使」　劉鳴煒：10歲生日收10萬現金，全部存銀行 (21:53)<br />\n<br />\n今晚播出的港台電視節目《講錢。講呢啲》，邀請青年發展委員會副主席、華人置業主席劉鳴煒訪問。主持任美貞問，當一個人金錢多得花不完，理財目的何在？劉鳴煒說，理財可以是個人紀律的延伸，沒有人希望身家「少咗幾個零」：「當你有細路仔、有屋企人、有想照顧的人，自然會想慢慢增值。」<br />\n<br />\n劉鳴煒在節目中提到，家庭教育教曉自己